00:00:15,990 --> 00:00:16,990
Thank you, honey.

3
00:00:19,870 --> 00:00:20,830
Ms. Ning Mochen.

4
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:47,250
On the day they fall into the lake,

5
00:00:47,270 --> 00:00:49,510
the world is drenched with torrential rain.

6
00:00:49,510 --> 00:00:50,950
At this critical moment...

7
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:52,350
They both manage to survive.

8
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:54,310
The main female character is reincarnated.

9
00:00:54,310 --> 00:00:57,710
She then triumphs over her enemies and finally changes her life, right?

10
00:00:57,710 --> 00:00:58,270
Yeah.

11
00:00:58,390 --> 00:00:59,670
I can always predict how this kind of story ends

12
00:00:59,670 --> 00:01:01,100
when I read the beginning of it.

13
00:01:01,100 --> 00:01:03,350
Didn't you tell me to write an exciting and dramatic story

14
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:04,510
where the main female character takes revenge?

15
00:01:04,510 --> 00:01:07,070
You also said the first few scenes had to be eye-catching,

16
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:08,039
and appealing to the readers

17
00:01:08,039 --> 00:01:09,390
so as to captivate their attention, right?

18
00:01:09,390 --> 00:01:11,990
Then where is the creative element I asked for?

19
00:01:13,670 --> 00:01:14,789
Where's the dramatic part?

20
00:01:14,789 --> 00:01:16,640
There has to be slumps before a rousing climax.

21
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,910
Rising from the lowest point brings the most joy.

22
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:20,870
Ms. Ai, I'm not being harsh here,

23
00:01:20,890 --> 00:01:22,430
but I just hope the beginning of the story

24
00:01:22,430 --> 00:01:23,910
contains all the elements I've asked for.

25
00:01:23,910 --> 00:01:25,710
I hope the readers can grasp the gist

26
00:01:25,710 --> 00:01:27,310
of this story at first sight.

27
00:01:27,310 --> 00:01:28,950
If I add every element you want into the story,

28
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,990
it'll only end up a huge mess

29
00:01:30,990 --> 00:01:32,520
that repulses the readers.

30
00:01:33,039 --> 00:01:37,240
But the project will be canceled if what you draw falls below expectations.

31
00:01:41,350 --> 00:01:43,680
Fine. I'll add a big twist to it right away.

32
